              "type": "text",
              "value": "Convolve the rank-2 input array with the separable filter defined by the rank-1 arrays hrow, and hcol. Mirror symmetric boundary conditions are assumed. This function can be used to find an image given its B-spline representation."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
